Langchain Demo with OpenAI API
This project demonstrates the integration of Langchain with OpenAI's GPT-3.5-turbo model using Streamlit for building a simple chatbot application.

Features
Streamlit Integration: A user-friendly web interface to interact with the chatbot.
Langchain Prompt Template: Utilizes Langchain's prompt templates for structured input.
OpenAI GPT-3.5-turbo: Leverages the powerful GPT-3.5-turbo model for generating responses.
Installation
Clone the repository:


git clone https://github.com/yourusername/your-repo-name.git
cd your-repo-name
Create and activate a virtual environment:


python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate  # On Windows
# source .venv/bin/activate  # On macOS/Linux
Install the required dependencies:


pip install -r requirements.txt
Environment Variables
Create a .env file in the root directory with the following content:

env
Copy code
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key
LANGCHAIN_API_KEY=your-langchain-api-key
LANGCHAIN_TRACING_V2=true
Running the Application
To run the Streamlit application, use the following command:

streamlit run app.py
Access the application in your browser at http://localhost:8501.

